    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286580/extras/854d77118d4416813d5e41cb981c22d5.avif?t=1751676263\" width=608 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Deer Crusade》是一款银河战士恶魔城类的2D冒险游戏，探索、战斗与解谜将引导你踏上归途。你将扮演一个被诅咒的孩子，在一个受玛雅神话启发的广袤神秘世界中寻找散落的宝石碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个精心打造的世界中，解锁强大的能力，挑战艰难的Boss，并发掘隐藏的秘密，体验充满环境叙事的冒险旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286580/extras/64fd39222e87bf174d7a7bfda5384edd.avif?t=1751676263\" width=608 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286580/extras/061cc54ca86a6a701caaa8fbe45d5b73.avif?t=1751676263\" width=608 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从激烈的战斗到安静的探索时刻，《Deer Crusade》邀请您踏上一场充满挑战且令人难忘的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286580/extras/4ac5807a9265443808f474b4e26edf93.avif?t=1751676263\" width=608 height=174 /></span></p>",
